{#   Purpose: This project implements a basic          #}
{#            feed slider that fetches data from       #}
{#            an existing Google+ profile. The         #}
{#            appearance as well as the data output    #}
{#            can be configured via the Gantry         #}
{#            templating framework.                    #}
